name: ONDA Swimmer
description:
ONDA is my first edition of my series "Swimmers"
She's also my first 3D swimmer (:
Accostumed to 2D illustrations, this was very new, difficult and super fun!
I love her and her crooked finger, let's welcome ONDA to the blockchain dimension
I hope she gets to swim on your wallet's waves 👀
Her friends are arriving soon!
